{
  "texts": [
    "We give an introduction to Hartree-Fock in Sec.",
    "3, beginning in general terms and then specializing to the TBG context in Sec.",
    "3.3; expert readers may choose to simply read this final section, perhaps skimming the rest to alert themselves to any idiosyncrasies of notation.",
    "We proceed to give a brief summary of the strong-coupling picture of TBG in Sec.",
    "4, and thereby introduce the chiral-flat limit where Hartree-Fock becomes exact at integer filling."
  ]
}